Thanks guys, going to do a workaround for this.  I&#39;m not happy with
having to hold down the button, or needing to reset.  I removed the
button pcb from the top half of the case tonight (including what looks
like a secondary antenna, the metal disc?), and removed the dome
contact from the up scan contact.  Going to run to radio shack
tomorrow and just solder a switch in to place on the trace contacts
(i.e. the contacts on the pcb that get connected when you press in the
dome piece).  Going to be putting everything in to its own project
setup anyways, so that&#39;s fine.

Marty

